== Further Reading == {{No footnotes|date=June 2018}} * *History of Wakayama City* (Wakayama City History Compilation Office) == See Also == * {{ill|Air raids on Japan|ja|日本本土空襲|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - Other locations in Wakayama Prefecture, such as {{ill|Shingū|ja|新宮空襲|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Kainan|ja|海南空襲|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, and {{ill|Tanabe|ja|田辺空襲|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, were also bombed. ''' {{ill|Gifu Air Raid|ja|岐阜空襲|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - Conducted almost simultaneously with the Wakayama Air Raid. ''' {{ill|Sendai Air Raid|ja|仙台空襲|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - Also occurred around the same time. ''' {{ill|Sakai Air Raid|ja|堺大空襲|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - Followed the Wakayama Air Raid in the early hours of July 10. * {{ill|War Victims Memorial Tower|ja|太平洋戦全国戦災都市空爆死没者慰霊塔|qq=draft|qq=draft}}
